jb_summer_v6 is an enhanced version which allows you to explore new games and uncover thrilling secrets.

The balance between Counter-Terrorists and Terrorists has been significantly adjusted.

Now prisoners have more rebellion variations but in the same time prisonguards have new some additional means to confront the rebel.

Furthermore, an annoying explosion was deleted from this map, ensuring an uninterrupted and immersive gaming experience for everyone.
